  "texts": [
    "However, its effectiveness heavily relies on the quality of the emulator.",
    "Defending against passive mode threats is more challenging because these attack strategies are often the result of the agent's own incomplete development and testing.",
    "Zhang et al. [207] integrated a homomorphic encryption scheme and deployed an attribute-based forgery generative model to safeguard against privacy breaches during communication processes.",
    "However, this approach incurs additional computational and communication costs for the agent.",
    "A more detailed discussion on related development and testing is presented in Section 4.1.2."
